{"tid":1747630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港抗爭成《經濟學人》封面","createTime":"2019-11-23T10:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T10:28:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a89a8e19e05725ea5a13cc815c91256bf60f98b1","tid":1747630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/WCTNHNCPQTADR7FN3JRIC5UXD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FWCTNHNCPQTADR7FN3JRIC5UXD4%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=84603541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FWCTNHNCPQTADR7FN3JRIC5UXD4%2F&h=24b664c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/WCTNHNCPQTADR7FN3JRIC5UXD4/</a><br />\n<br />\n港抗爭成《經濟學人》封面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/rspRgH6XtGjB-r_b-lTDnA8ca8c=/802x1046/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NAWJVAE2NBY7UBDXWUH65JUKVM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FrspRgH6XtGjB-r_b-lTDnA8ca8c%3D%2F802x1046%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNAWJVAE2NBY7UBDXWUH65JUKVM.gif&h=14165159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《經濟學人》以抗爭者為封面，指撤回逃犯條例對回復社會平靜效果輕微。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反修例風波引起全球注視，香港的逆權抗爭登上最新一期《經濟學人》封面，標題為「Hong Kong in revolt（香港起義）」，副題「China's unruly periphery（中國不治之疆）」。文章指出，即使抗爭者有暴力行為，公眾仍然予以強烈的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為爭取民主抗爭料持續<br />\n<br />\n最新一期《經濟學人》封面文章指出，香港抗爭五個月，幸未有大規模的流血事件，即使抗爭者有破壞和投擲汽油彈的暴力行為，社會仍然強烈支持抗爭者，區議會選舉將會是民意的測試，以及打擊親建制陣營的一個機會。<br />\n<br />\n文章並提到，港府撤回逃犯條例修訂的讓步，對回復社會平靜的效果輕微，示威者希望爭取民主，預視抗爭會持續。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，北京不急於出動解放軍鎮壓，並引述知情人士指，北京不希望沾手香港問題，因為在全球金融中心向民眾開槍的政治及經濟代價龐大。<br />\n<br />\n文章分析，中國國家主席習近平在操控上的殘暴和不妥協作風，令香港及其他中國邊界地區人民憤怒，傾向獨立的台灣民進黨料在台灣人擔心失去民主下，會在明年初總統選舉中有好表現，而新疆「再教育營」文件曝光，更可見中共精英非全面認同習的強硬路線，問題隨時快速擴散至中央。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾偉龍"},{"pid":"c4e5c62670388a991fc6ab9f6d505ac618e7b5c3","tid":1747630,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">區議會選舉將會是民意的測試，以及打擊親建制陣營的一個機會。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果輸左<br />\n白票撚對家撚唔好問點解外國人唔再支持你地"},{"pid":"fde6334cdca0f09da66acc539536c4ddac1fb4fd","tid":1747630,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d20a2ca15efeaf07928cd0c3ddc6955c27f14562","tid":1747630,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"當大家仲好有原則咁話個game唔公平<br />\n有大bug<br />\n唔投依個唔投嗰個<br />\n<br />\n甚至投保皇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信保皇同中共已開定香檳<br />\n統一戰線大成功<br />\n<br />\n用反間計離間計<br />\n<br />\n不戰而勝<br />\n<br />\n全世界傳媒，議員開哂口話今次係變相公投<br />\n世界各國傳媒喺香港 議員嚟觀察<br />\n<br />\n但香港人畢竟多政治白痴<br />\n喺受薪三毛 分化撚橫行嘅鋪天蓋地宣傳下<br />\n唔團結 好有原則 好冇策略<br />\n對住個狡猾同最叻玩政治，最叻分化嘅政權 <br />\n條路自己揀<br />\n仆街唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n唉 我只係覺得好可惜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果輸咗<br />\n萬劫不復<br />\n<br />\n一定投反建制<br />\n得建制同熱狗對決 就為大局投lesser evil 熱狗<br />\n<br />\n大家聽日早啲去投票<br />\n全家總動員<br />\nCall齊親友</span>"},{"pid":"824ed0e6982a4ff3ffebc56097dffc571d571664","tid":1747630,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc6c8c23768611fc6ca3737ae6b4720ab30f28f","tid":1747630,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/WCTNHNCPQTADR7FN3JRIC5UXD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FWCTNHNCPQTADR7FN3JRIC5UXD4%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=84603541\" d